Package uniol.apt.module Description

The module interface allowing to separate the implementation of an algorithm from the user interface. Implementations of Module annotated with AptModule are automatically picked up and can be used. It is strongly recommended for modules to inherit from AbstractModule to simplify the implementation of the Module interface.
